<s> For most of these items, no, there isn't any default you can supply.  </s>
<s> With one exception: you can supply a default "alt" attribute for images.  </s>
<s> See the "alt-text" option: take it easy, Charlie  </s>
<s> FWIW, summary is not *required* for [x]HTML validity.  </s>
<s> Yes, Tidy gives you warnings for each table lacking a summary -- and it's a good idea (unless, IMO, the table is for layout purposes), but you can run pages with tables omitting summary through an [x]HTML validator without any objections.  </s>
